OL,3,CWales great Leigh Halfpenny to retire
OL,4,Cfrom rugby
OL,6,FWales rugby legend Leigh Halfpenny has
OL,7,Fannounced he will retire at the end of
OL,8,Fthe season, bringing down the curtain
OL,9,Fon a professional career spanning
OL,10,Falmost two decades.
OL,12,FThe 37-year-old won the last of his
OL,13,F101 caps in 2023 and made four Test
OL,14,Fappearances across three British &
OL,15,FIrish Lions tours, winning player of
OL,16,Fthe series in the 2013 triumph over
OL,17,FAustralia.
