OL,3,CWales great Leigh Halfpenny to retire
OL,4,Cfrom rugby
OL,6,FHis senior club career began at
OL,7,FCardiff in 2008 and will now end at
OL,8,FArms Park after he rejoined the Welsh
OL,9,Fregion last summer.
OL,11,FHalfpenny had also played for Toulon,
OL,12,FScarlets and Harlequins, among others.
OL,14,F"It's inevitable that every player
OL,15,Fcomes to the end of their career, but
OL,16,FI am genuinely saddened to see Leigh
OL,17,Ffinish this season," Cardiff Rugby
OL,18,Flife president Sir Gareth Edwards said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@TO]
