OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778076676
OL,3,CWales great Leigh Halfpenny to retire
OL,4,Cfrom rugby
OL,6,F"He has achieved so much in the game
OL,7,Fand undoubtedly goes down as one of
OL,8,Fthe game's greatest players.
OL,10,F"He is someone I have admired,
OL,11,Frespected and enjoying watching over
OL,12,Fthe years, and even more so as a
OL,13,Fplayer from Cardiff.
OL,15,F"Off the pitch, his personality also
OL,16,Fmakes him such a likeable young man.
OL,17,FHe is so humble and always has time
OL,18,Ffor people, even in the chaos
OL,19,Fsometimes brought by his stature in
OL,20,Fthe game."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU|D@JO]
